'''牛奶蛇'''（學名：''Lampropeltis triangulum''；{{lang-en|milk snake、milksnake}}）是[[王蛇属|王蛇属]]的一種無毒蛇<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.biokids.umich.edu/critters/Lampropeltis_triangulum/|title=BioKIDS – Kids' Inquiry of Diverse Species, Lampropeltis triangulum, Scarlet kingsnake|first=Animal Diversity|last=Web|website=www.biokids.umich.edu|accessdate=2020-03-23|archive-date=2020-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200323065550/http://www.biokids.umich.edu/critters/Lampropeltis_triangulum/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.esf.edu/pubprog/brochure/snakes/snakes.htm|title=Snakes of New York|website=SUNY College of Environmental Science and Forestry|accessdate=2020-03-23|archive-date=2020-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200517193010/https://www.esf.edu/pubprog/brochure/snakes/snakes.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，有24个[[亚种|亚种]]，每个亚种的外形相差很大，有的分类学家主张将其分为几个不同的[[种|种]]<ref name="Grzimek">{{citation
